==English==
=== Intransitive verb ===

# to assume a sitting position from a position lying down
#: ''Despite being sick, Lorin sat up once he heard the news''

=== Transitive verb ===

# to set into a sitting position (from a lying-down position)
#: ''I sat the coma patient up so she could watch TV''

=== Noun ===

#alternative spelling of [[sit-up]]

